        <updateDate>2021-08-02T20:11:00Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Telling Everyone the Location of data Leaving the U.S. Act or the TELL Act</b><br /><br />This bill requires online sellers or distributors of mobile applications that maintain and store information in China to conspicuously disclose to users that such information is stored in&nbsp;China and whether the information is accessible by the Chinese Communist Party or a Chinese state-owned entity. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
